Tyrael sat at his desk. As Shadow Star enters, the door automatically 
closes behind him (auto-doors, no tricks if you ask).

Tyrael:What I have to say has to remain between us only. I presume 
that Megatron has gone back to prehistoric Earth and that those 
foolish Maximals followed him. We have to remain a secret 
organization, and in this goal, we have to eradicate anyone who comes 
in contact with our group before we are to leave. Also, we have to 
learn what the Predacons are up to. I will leave this to you. 
Questions?
